      </h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">
        <!-- Zakat Guide -->
        <div
          class="bg-white rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300"
        >
          <img
            src="/assets/images/home.jpg"
            alt="Zakat Guide"
            class="w-full h-48 object-cover"
          />
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-4 text-green-800">Zakat Guide</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-6">
              Learn more about Zakat and how to calculate it.
            </p>
            <button
              class="bg-green-600 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-lg w-full hover:bg-green-700 transition-all duration-300"
            >
              Learn More
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Zakat Calculator -->
        <div
          class="bg-white rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300"
        >
          <img
            src="/assets/images/home.jpg"
            alt="Zakat Calculator"
            class="w-full h-48 object-cover"
          />
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-4 text-green-800">
              Zakat Calculator
            </h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-6">
              Use our Zakat calculator to work out how much you owe.
            </p>
            <button
              class="bg-green-600 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-lg w-full hover:bg-green-700 transition-all duration-300"
            >
              Calculate Now
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Zakat Appeal -->
        <div
          class="bg-white rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300"
        >
          <img
            src="/assets/images/home.jpg"
            alt="Zakat Appeal"
            class="w-full h-48 object-cover"
          />
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-4 text-green-800">Zakat Appeal</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-6">
              Give your Zakat to help those most in need.
            </p>
            <button
              class="bg-green-600 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-lg w-full hover:bg-green-700 transition-all duration-300"
            >
              Donate Now
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Statistics section -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div
          class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300"
        >
          <div
            class="bg-red-600 text-white px-3 py-1 text-sm rounded-full inline-block mb-4"
          >
            Â£2.5 PO
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-green-800">
            Zakat Can Feed a Family
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            Your Zakat can feed a family of four for two weeks, providing
            life-saving food.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300"
        >
          <div
            class="bg-pink-600 text-white px-3 py-1 text-sm rounded-full inline-block mb-4"
          >
            2.5%
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-green-800">
            Distributing Your Wealth
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            Zakat is 2.5% of wealth owned over 1 year for those who meet the
            nisab threshold.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300"
        >
          <div
            class="bg-red-600 text-white px-3 py-1 text-sm rounded-full inline-block mb-4"
          >
            6.9 MILL
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-green-800">
            People Who Received Zakat
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            Zakat has provided over 6.9 million meals to those in need over the
            past 5 years.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12 lg:py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <!-- Blog Section Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center mb-3 px-4 py-1 bg-gray-100 rounded-full">
          <span class="text-[#E31E24] font-medium text-sm">Blog & News</span>
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="ml-2">
            <path d="M8 0C3.6 0 0 3.6 0 8C0 12.4 3.6 16 8 16C12.4 16 16 12.4 16 8C16 3.6 12.4 0 8 0ZM9 12H7V7H9V12ZM8 5.5C7.2 5.5 6.5 4.8 6.5 4C6.5 3.2 7.2 2.5 8 2.5C8.8 2.5 9.5 3.2 9.5 4C9.5 4.8 8.8 5.5 8 5.5Z" fill="#E31E24"></path>
